    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"张小伦的网络日志","description":"欢迎来到张小伦的网络日志 \n\t\t一个记录生活，分享心得的博客","menu":[{"id":"home","name":"首页","url":"/"},{"id":"blog","name":"博文","url":"/blogs"},{"id":"category","name":"分类","url":"/categories"},{"id":"archive","name":"归档","url":"/archives"},{"id":"lab","name":"实验室","url":"/labs"},{"id":"about","name":"关于我","url":"/about"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6763422f-533d-5578-a174-e3d3991ec1af","html":"<p class=\"para\">###pip的安装</p>\n<p class=\"para\">先下载一个 python 文件 : <a href=\"https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py\" class=\"link-underline\">get-pip.py</a>。\r\n然后运行下面这条命令（可能需要管理员权限）：</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">python get-pip.py</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p class=\"para\">如果 <a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools\" class=\"link-underline\">setuptools</a> 还没有安装，pip会帮你安装。如果想更新已经存在的 setuptools，只要运行</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">pip install -U setuptools</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p class=\"para\">为了确保能够在命令行中使用 <code>pip</code> 命令，确保将 Python 安装目录中的 <code>Scripts</code> 文件夹路径添加到系统的环境变量中。这个必须手动添加！</p>\n<p class=\"para\">###升级 pip</p>\n<p class=\"para\">在 Linux 或者 Mac 中：</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">pip install -U pip</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p class=\"para\">在 Window 中：</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">python -m pip install -U pip</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p class=\"para\">###安装 packages</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">$ pip install SomePackage            # latest version\r\n$ pip install SomePackage==1.0.4     # specific version\r\n$ pip install &#39;SomePackage&gt;=1.0.4&#39;     # minimum version</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p class=\"para\">###卸载 packages</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">    $ pip install SomePackage</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p class=\"para\">所以，在成功安装了 pip之后，可以使用 pip 安装 Django</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">pip install Django==1.6.5</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>","tableOfContents":"","headings":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"利用pip安装Django","date":"2014-07-12","cover":null,"description":null,"categories":["Python"],"tags":["Python"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blogs/git使用笔记(一)/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Git 使用笔记(一)-入门级的操作"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blogs/(译)取消事件冒泡的危害/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"(译)阻止事件传播的危害","tags":["译文","JavaScript"],"categories":[],"status":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"6763422f-533d-5578-a174-e3d3991ec1af","previousPostId":"3ffa5f00-9101-5bf7-8e31-69205c8d5aa4","nextPostId":"f9448968-cbfe-53a8-a14e-57742cbdf09b"}},
